<% layout('/layouts/boilerplate') %>
<% locals.showBackBtn = true; %>

  <style>
    .legal-page {
      max-width: 780px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2.5rem 1rem 3rem;
    }

    .legal-page h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .legal-page .legal-meta {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .legal-section {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .legal-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
      padding-left: 0.75rem;
    }

    .legal-section p,
    .legal-section li {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .legal-section ul {
      padding-left: 1.4rem;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .legal-divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--bg-tertiary);
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
    }

    .legal-nav {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .legal-nav a {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      color: var(--text-dark);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background var(--transition-fast), color var(--transition-fast);
    }

    .legal-nav a:hover,
    .legal-nav a.active {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #fff;
    }
  </style>

  <div class="legal-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="legal-meta">Last updated: January 2025 &middot; Effective immediately</p>

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>1. What We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you use Rentlyst, we may collect the following types of information:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Account Data</strong>: Your name, email address, and profile information provided during sign-up
        </li>
        <li><strong>Listing Data</strong>: Content, images, descriptions, and metadata you submit in your listings</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data</strong>: Pages visited, search queries, device type, and browser type</li>
        <li><strong>Communications</strong>: Messages sent between users through the Platform's messaging system</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider">

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information collected to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Operate, maintain, and improve the Rentlyst platform</li>
        <li>Display your profile and listings to other users</li>
        <li>Enable messaging and communication between users</li>
        <li>Power AI-driven features such as the Rentlyst Agent assistant</li>
        <li>Send important account and service-related notifications</li>
        <li>Detect and prevent fraud, spam, or abuse</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider">

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>Rentlyst does <strong>not sell</strong> your personal data to third parties. We may share data with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Service Providers</strong>: Trusted vendors that help us run the platform (cloud hosting, image
          storage, authentication)</li>
        <li><strong>Legal Requirements</strong>: When required by law or to protect the rights, property, or safety of
          Rentlyst or its users</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Your listing content (title, images, price) is public by design and visible to all visitors.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider">

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>4. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
      <p>We use session cookies to keep you logged in and to remember your preferences. We do not use third-party
        advertising trackers. You may disable cookies in your browser settings, though this may affect your ability to
        use certain features.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider">

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain your data for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide services. You may request
        deletion of your account and associated data by contacting us through the <a href="/help"
          class="legal-link">Help Center</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider">

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>6. Security</h2>
      <p>We implement industry-standard security measures including encrypted connections (HTTPS), hashed authentication
        tokens, and access controls. However, no online platform can guarantee absolute security. Use the Platform at
        your own risk.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider">

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Rentlyst is not intended for individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect data from children.
        If you believe a minor has created an account, please contact us immediately via the <a href="/help"
          class="legal-link">Help Center</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="legal-divider">

    <div class="legal-section">
      <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify registered users of material changes by
        email or by a notice on the Platform. Please review this page periodically.</p>
    </div>
  </div>